{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1280,"text":"What does it mean to be a witness?"},{"time":5560,"text":"Why is it important to bear witness"},{"time":8400,"text":"to people's suffering,"},{"time":10400,"text":"especially when those people\nare isolated from us?"},{"time":15440,"text":"And what happens when we turn away?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":20000,"text":"Three years ago, I traveled\nto the Central African Republic"},{"time":23680,"text":"to report on its ongoing war."},{"time":26920,"text":"I'd heard warnings of massacres"},{"time":29720,"text":"in the country's jungles and deserts,"},{"time":33440,"text":"but no one could locate these massacres"},{"time":36240,"text":"or tell me who was killed, or when."},{"time":41520,"text":"I drove into this war"},{"time":44200,"text":"with little information."},{"time":46640,"text":"I witnessed scenes\nthat were tragic and unreal,"},{"time":51840,"text":"and only at the end did I realize"},{"time":54080,"text":"that I had witnessed\nthe slow preparation of ethnic cleansing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":62160,"text":"The Central African Republic\nis a country of about five million people"},{"time":66080,"text":"the size of Texas"},{"time":67600,"text":"in the center of Africa."},{"time":70240,"text":"The country has known chronic violence\nsince French colonial rule ended in 1960."},{"time":76440,"text":"The war I reported on"},{"time":78400,"text":"was between the minority\nMuslim government,"},{"time":81520,"text":"called the Seleka,"},{"time":83920,"text":"and citizen militias,"},{"time":86080,"text":"mostly Christian,"},{"time":87880,"text":"called the anti-balaka."}]},{"cues":[{"time":92360,"text":"The first sign of the impending cleansing"},{"time":95400,"text":"was the breakdown of trust\nwithin communities."},{"time":100040,"text":"Three days after I arrived in the country,"},{"time":102960,"text":"I watched the small city\nof Gaga be abandoned."},{"time":107560,"text":"A battle was about to break out."},{"time":110280,"text":"And to save themselves,"},{"time":111960,"text":"many people were working\nas government spies,"},{"time":115880,"text":"identifying friends and neighbors"},{"time":119320,"text":"to be killed."},{"time":122960,"text":"Cities and towns,"},{"time":125240,"text":"any place with humans, had become unsafe."},{"time":130120,"text":"So people moved to the jungle."},{"time":133960,"text":"I felt strangely isolated"},{"time":137240,"text":"as pigs and livestock\nmoved into the empty homes."},{"time":144080,"text":"In a war zone,"},{"time":145600,"text":"you know that you are near the killing\nwhen people have left."}]},{"cues":[{"time":150800,"text":"The war moved across the jungle\nand reached Gaga,"},{"time":153560,"text":"and I was surrounded\nby the thunder of bombs."},{"time":157000,"text":"Government forces drove into the jungle\nto attack a town sheltering a militia."},{"time":164560,"text":"I rode on motorcycle for hours,"},{"time":167080,"text":"crossing jungle streams\nand tall elephant grass,"},{"time":171280,"text":"but I only got to the town"},{"time":173320,"text":"after the government had burned it"},{"time":175200,"text":"and its people were gone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":178400,"text":"To see if I could speak to someone,"},{"time":180120,"text":"I shouted out that I was a friend,\nthat I would not hurt them."},{"time":184680,"text":"A woman in a red shirt\nran out of the forest."},{"time":189400,"text":"Others cautiously emerged from the trees"},{"time":192560,"text":"and asked, \"Est-ce les gens savent?\""},{"time":196200,"text":"\"Do people know?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":198960,"text":"The question surprised me."},{"time":200800,"text":"Their children were hungry and sick,"},{"time":203280,"text":"but they didn't ask for food or medicine."},{"time":206520,"text":"They asked me,"},{"time":208120,"text":"\"Do people know what is happening to us?\""},{"time":213440,"text":"I felt helpless\nas I wrote down their question."},{"time":217680,"text":"And I became determined"},{"time":220960,"text":"that this moment in their lives"},{"time":224280,"text":"should not be forgotten."},{"time":227480,"text":"In bearing witness to their crisis,"},{"time":229840,"text":"I felt a small communion\nwith these people."},{"time":234000,"text":"From far away, this war had felt\nlike a footnote in world news."},{"time":241120,"text":"As a witness,"},{"time":242880,"text":"the war felt like history unfolding."}]},{"cues":[{"time":246840,"text":"The government denied\nthat it was committing any violence,"},{"time":250400,"text":"but I continually drove through towns"},{"time":253440,"text":"where people described\ngovernment massacres"},{"time":256440,"text":"from a day or a week before."}]},{"cues":[{"time":261240,"text":"I felt overwhelmed"},{"time":263480,"text":"and tried to calm myself."},{"time":266280,"text":"As I reported on these massacres,"},{"time":268800,"text":"I bought and ate"},{"time":271520,"text":"little sweets,"},{"time":273560,"text":"seeking the familiar\ncomfort of their taste."},{"time":279880,"text":"Central Africans ate these sweets"},{"time":282040,"text":"to ease their hunger,"},{"time":284560,"text":"leaving a trail of thousands\nof plastic wrappers as they fled."}]},{"cues":[{"time":290680,"text":"On the few radio stations\nstill operating in the country,"},{"time":294680,"text":"I mostly heard pop music."},{"time":298680,"text":"As the war mounted,"},{"time":300720,"text":"we received less information\nabout the massacres."},{"time":304360,"text":"It became easier\nto feel a sense of normalcy."},{"time":312080,"text":"I witnessed the effect\nof this missing information."},{"time":316560,"text":"Two weeks later, I slowly and anxiously"},{"time":320480,"text":"drove into an isolated\nmilitia headquarters,"},{"time":323680,"text":"a town called PK100."},{"time":326680,"text":"Here, Christian fighters told me"},{"time":329640,"text":"that all Muslims were foreigners,"},{"time":332200,"text":"evil and allied with the government."},{"time":335920,"text":"They likened Muslims to animals."},{"time":340480,"text":"Without neutral observers or media"},{"time":343600,"text":"to counter this absurd narrative,"},{"time":346160,"text":"it became the single narrative\nin these camps."},{"time":350600,"text":"The militias began to hunt down Muslims,"},{"time":353280,"text":"and emptied the capital, Bangui,"},{"time":356160,"text":"of nearly 140,000 Muslims"},{"time":359000,"text":"in just a few months."},{"time":362760,"text":"Most of the killing and fleeing of Muslims\nwent unrecorded by witnesses."}]},{"cues":[{"time":370640,"text":"I'm telling you about my reporting\nin the Central African Republic,"},{"time":375040,"text":"but I still ask myself why I went there."},{"time":379080,"text":"Why put myself at risk?"},{"time":382600,"text":"I do this work"},{"time":383920,"text":"because I feel that ignored people\nin all our communities"},{"time":389360,"text":"tell us something important"},{"time":391400,"text":"about who we are."},{"time":396000,"text":"When information is missing,"},{"time":398280,"text":"people have the power\nto manipulate reality."},{"time":403320,"text":"Without witnesses,"},{"time":405560,"text":"we would believe that those thousands\nof massacred people are still alive,"},{"time":410280,"text":"that those hundreds\nof burned homes are still standing."},{"time":414360,"text":"A war zone can pass"},{"time":416040,"text":"for a mostly peaceful place"},{"time":418320,"text":"when no one is watching."},{"time":422080,"text":"And a witness can become precious,"},{"time":425680,"text":"and their gaze most necessary,"},{"time":428480,"text":"when violence passes silently,"},{"time":433000,"text":"unseen and unheard."}]},{"cues":[{"time":435960,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":437200,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}